{
  "stem": "25288.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it took it about two-- two years till the Yad Vashem-- oh.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I didn't-- I was looking for his-- there-- for-- for this woman, for the wife of this commander officer.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we find out from Budapest, they move to Miskolc.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we didn't know the house-- the-- the address.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We know it's Kubini.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were looking in the telephone book.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was two Kubini in the telephone book in Miskolc.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we call up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one-- one of 'em, yes, I'm-- I'm the-- I'm the son of this-- this-- it's old-time Kubini.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But my mother passed away several years ago.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- I said, I recommended to the-- to the Yad Vashem and described, he's not-- of course, he's not alive, but his son is here.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he would deserve some recognition.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they asked paper to-- to prove he is really his son.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He have to send that in, the birth certificate from the father, and his certificate.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was so much we did.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I wouldn't say that's so much, because I was happy to do it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And finally, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] then, finally it came.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a recognition day in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they call up this young Kubini.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His name is Martin Kubini-- call up, and asked him to come in Budapest, and with a nice-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] they presented him with a certificate and a nice medal for his father.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't see the medal all the way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- I-- but my daughter was there-- not in that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he was in Tokaj, and he meeted this young man, and he-- she saw this medal-- medal and-- and the certificate.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that's how it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's all I could do.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
